                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; color: var(--text);">My Journey</h3>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--muted);">Discover how I got started, what excites me, and my continuous learning process.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="flex: 1; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1rem; background: #fff;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; color: var(--text);">Future Plans</h3>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--muted);">Check out my learning plans and aspirations for the future.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card" style="flex: 1; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1rem; background: #fff;">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; color: var(--text);">Contact Me</h3>
                    <p style="line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--muted);">Feel free to reach out to me for collaboration, feedback, or just to say hi.</p>
